title: The Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show Podcast
itunes:title: The Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show Podcast
description:
PODCAST SUMMARY HOUR 1:

Biden blames Texas, Florida for new covid infections, DeSantis fires back. Defund the police activist Rep. Cori Bush says she wants to defund the police and keep her private security. Rep. Elise Stefanik on why she thinks Cuomo will be impeached. Psaki tries to clean up Biden's mess on the unconstitutional eviction moratorium.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
